name: Never mind
body:
There are no code changes in this release. It only changes build process for [the Rust library](https://crates.io/crates/imagequant). 

For anyone that already has pngquant compiled, this release doesn't do anything.

name: Rusty
body: This is the first release that can be built using Rust.
Please see [the website](https://pngquant.org/) for releases and downloads.
